service.tut.pori.contentstorage

Class MediaList

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
      • service.tut.pori.contentstorage.MediaList

  • public class MediaList
extends ResponseData
    This is a container class for media elements, which can be used directly with Response to provide XML output.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<mediaList>
  <media>
    <UID>90f53588-a87c-4800-a2cd-bcc9e3ee85bb</UID>
    <serviceId>7</serviceId>
    <visibility>PUBLIC</visibility>
    <mediaType>VIDEO</mediaType>
    <userId>6723916233463126098</userId>
    <url>http://fe.example.org/rest/vca/r?uid=90f53588-a87c-4800-a2cd-bcc9e3ee85bb&amp;service_id=7</url>
  </media>
</mediaList>
